strings: <voice_0x01001299><se_high>Jessica: Ever since we defeated Dhoulmagus and I picked up the sceptre, I haven't been able to speak my own mind.
<voice_0x0100129A><se_high>Jessica: So I just wanted to say this now: I don't feel like I've avenged my brother's death at all.

<voice_0x0100129B><se_high>Jessica: I don't know who or what this Lord of Darkness, Rhapthorne is, but we can't afford
to relax while the sceptre is still missing.

<voice_0x0100129C><se_high>Jessica: I don't intend to stop searching until we've found that sceptre and sealed Rhapthorne
away again.
<voice_0x0100129D><se_high>Jessica: So...er...I guess we'll be spending a lot more time together.
<voice_0x0100129E><se_high>Jessica: ...Sorry, did that come out a bit strange?
<voice_0x0100129F><se_high>Jessica: Oh yeah? Well, at least I don't LOOK strange! You should look in a mirror sometime, <hero>!

<voice_0x010012A0><se_high>Jessica: Really? Thanks, <hero>.
You're sweet, you know that?
